                        <p class="sans-serif-body-2 text-classic-grey">
                        Adidas is a global leader in sportswear and digital innovation. While the brand already had strong content and high online conversion rates, their product-related content and e-commerce experience existed in isolation from each other. Product pages were not always directly linked to the content that promoted them, and content pages lacked intuitive pathways for customers to shop the featured products.
                        <br><br>
                        Adidas needed to create a seamless experience that bridged the gap between product information and brand content. The goal was to combine the two in a way that felt cohesive and organic, enhancing the user journey without disrupting it. The brand wanted to offer a fully branded experience, allowing customers to move fluidly from discovering content to completing a purchase.
