                        <br><br>
                        To address this, we proposed the creation of an innovative Product Listing Page (PLP) that integrated brand content and provided users with the option to toggle between ‚Äòstory mode‚Äô and a traditional grid layout. Additionally, we re-imagined the image gallery on product detail pages and introduced interactive, shoppable video content. This would allow customers to interact with content while simultaneously viewing or purchasing products.
